data.description: Convenient location just blocks from all services in Bingen, WA.   4 bedroom home with oversized garage offers incredible space for you and all your gorge toys! Daylight basement offers spacious family room, private bedroom, laundry, full bath and great storage. Upper level with open living concept offers an inviting area for entertianing and it opens to the back deck the expands the opportunity to have large gatherings. Primary ensuite, 2 guests beds and full bath complete the upper floor. The 100' x 100' lot is comprised of 2 legal parcels. Fenced back yard. Large back decks off the kitchen and primary suite. Newer roof.
